    <title>CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇/2019-11-03_CentOS 7 Minimal架站技術篇(二)  安裝SSH+使用Putty連線至安裝好的CentOS 7終端機</title>
    <url>/2019/11/03/CentOS%207%20Minimal%E6%9E%B6%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%AF%87/2019-11-03_CentOS%207%20Minimal%E6%9E%B6%E7%AB%99%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E7%AF%87(%E4%BA%8C)%20%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9DSSH+%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Putty%E9%80%A3%E7%B7%9A%E8%87%B3%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84CentOS%207%E7%B5%82%E7%AB%AF%E6%A9%9F/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>#應用軟體準備<br>Putty下載連結處<br><a href="https://www.chiark.greenend.org.uk/~sgtatham/putty/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.chiark.greenend.org.uk/~sgtatham/putty/</a></p>
<p>#先在Windows 10作業環境下安裝Putty<br>1、根據PC作業系統,選擇32-bit或64-bit下載完後並安裝<br><img src="/images/15733964492586.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>2、安裝步驟就不一一截圖了，就一直下一步就完成了，如真的不行，就Google搜尋「Putty安裝教學」就有可以參考嚕！</p>
<p>3、安裝完成後，開啟軟體如下圖畫面即可<br><img src="/images/15733965912746.jpg" alt=""></p>
<p>##開始至前篇所建立好的虛擬主機上安裝SSH服務</p>
